      <guid>https://www.eugeniovaldano.com/event/2023scalesworkshop/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;We are organizing this workshop which is a joint effort of the working groups Mesoscopic Scales of Epidemic Dynamics (coordinated by Eugenio) and Modeling of Within-Host Dynamics of the &lt;a href=&#34;https://anrs.fr/fr/recherche/groupes-animation-scientifique/ac-modelisation/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Action Coordonnée Modélisation des maladies infectieuses&lt;/a&gt; of the &lt;a href=&#34;https://anrs.fr/fr/recherche/groupes-animation-scientifique/ac-modelisation/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;ANRS-MIE&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.inserm.fr/en/home/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;INSERM&lt;/a&gt; agency for the research on HIV, TB, STI, viral hepatitis and emerging and re-emerging infectious diseases).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our speakers will be Laura Alessandretti, Federico Baldo, Luca Dall&amp;rsquo;Asta, Raluca Eftimie, Raphaël Forien, Simon Gubbins, Jérémie Guedj, Jose Ramasco.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Check out the full program program and register for free on the &lt;a href=&#34;https://thescalesofepimodeling.weebly.com/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;website of the event&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This workshop is funded by the AC Modélisation des maladies infectieuses of the ANRS-MIE.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
